{"tid":1769624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動Post，請幫推] 愛丁堡集會 - 全民聲討濫放催淚彈","createTime":"2019-12-05T04:18:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T04:25:27.000Z","uid":38842,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cf8af23b0770e1d675f4dd9b4b1ae8443a7bff6f","tid":1769624,"uid":38842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T04:18:38.000Z","msg":"反送中運動，有多少次令你流下眼淚？<br />\n因看見警暴而感到憤恨悲傷嗎?<br />\n因在困苦環境看見人性光輝而感動嗎?<br />\n<br />\n猶記得五年前雨傘革命，當時警察用了幾枚催淚彈，已經引起社會極大反響。可是今天，警方竟施放超過一萬枚催淚彈，向和平示威者瞄頭發放、在老人院附近發放、在密閉空間內發放、甚至在四處無人的街道中發放，竟成了常態。<br />\n<br />\n關於催淚煙對人體和環境的危險，已不斷有專家痛陳。但政府和警隊深明一個道理，就是只要不合理的事每天發生，人類便會開始習慣。但正因此，我們不能麻木！<br />\n<br />\n一群來自中大和教大的言語治療學系學生，邀請了化學家和醫生等專家，於12月6日 (明晚)在愛丁堡廣場舉行集會，聚焦催淚煙對人體的影響。<br />\n不斷的遊行集會已有半年，大家或許有點累，但休息？不了。現在放棄的話我們將失去一切。<br />\n<br />\n請一起到愛丁堡廣場見面！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100707421405291/posts/114552663354100?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100707421405291%2Fposts%2F114552663354100%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=nBH2CsHB%2BCaOzcOtxJw1e%2FYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=59bfdba2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100707421405291/posts/114552663354100?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n主辦單位：言語有時<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/timetospeakhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftimetospeakhk%2F&d=nBH2CsHB%2BCaOzcOtxJw1e%2FYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=df99a72e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/timetospeakhk/</a><br />\n請大家俾個LIKE啲學生！"},{"pid":"0da4cdb66ea4f4a3f9d28aaabb152f84ffdc28fe","tid":1769624,"uid":38842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T04:21:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/udMwLuX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FudMwLuX.jpg&h=349ca191&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hzzm7Jh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHzzm7Jh.jpg&h=3